OL,3,CSecurity alert after car 'explosion'
OL,4,Coutside police station
OL,6,FA security alert is under way in
OL,7,FDunmurry in Northern Ireland after
OL,8,Freports of a car explosion outside a
OL,9,Fpolice station.
OL,11,FHomes in the area, which is on the
OL,12,Foutskirts of Belfast, have been
OL,13,Fevacuated and members of the public
OL,14,Fhave been advised to avoid the scene.
OL,16,FIt is thought there have been no
OL,17,Finjuries.
OL,19,FSinn Fein Assembly member for the area
OL,20,FDanny Baker expressed concern in a
OL,21,Fpost on social media.
OL,26,@{D@Grr
