OL,3,CSecurity alert after car 'explosion'
OL,4,Coutside police station
OL,6,F"There have been reports of an
OL,7,Fexplosion close to the Dunmurry police
OL,8,Fstation," he said.
OL,10,F"I would ask anyone travelling in that
OL,11,Fdirection to avoid the area and if
OL,12,Fresidents need support, to get in
OL,13,Ftouch.
OL,15,F"At this stage, there is very little
OL,16,Finformation, and I hope no-one is
OL,17,Fhurt."
