OL,3,CSecurity alert after car 'explosion'
OL,4,Coutside police station
OL,6,FLagan Valley MP Sorcha Eastwood said
OL,7,Fit was a car bomb which had been left
OL,8,Fclose to homes and businesses saying
OL,9,Fit was "distressing and disturbing".
OL,10,FShe said ther
OL,12,F"A busy area, a car bomb left outside
OL,13,Fresidential housing, small businesses
OL,14,Fand any number of people out and about
OL,15,Fon a Saturday night working or
OL,16,Fsocialising.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
