OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777205471
OL,3,CSecurity alert after car 'explosion'
OL,4,Coutside police station
OL,6,F"It is only through the grace of God
OL,7,Fthat there are no casualties. I'm
OL,8,Freally grateful to the first
OL,9,Fresponders, PSNI and Army Technical
OL,10,FOfficers as well as other emergency
OL,11,Fservices who attended the scene.
OL,13,F"The good and decent people of
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland, from right across
OL,15,Fall communities, rejected the bomb and
OL,16,Fthe bullet in the past and will do so
OL,17,Fagain. We are stronger than you and
OL,18,Fany evil you may seek to wreak across
OL,19,Four community. You will never win."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
