OL,3,CSecurity alert after car 'explosion'
OL,4,Coutside police station
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Police Service of
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland said: "Police are
OL,8,Fcurrently at the scene of a security
OL,9,Falert in the Kingsway area of Dunmurry
OL,10,Fthis morning, Sunday April 26.
OL,12,F"Members of the public are asked to
OL,13,Favoid the area. Cordons are in place
OL,14,Fand an evacuation operation is under
OL,15,Fway.
OL,17,F"An update will follow in due course."
OL,26,@oD@XOUtD@AOUyD@AOUyD@fO]
