OL,3,CSecurity alert after car 'explosion'
OL,4,Coutside police station
OL,6,FLast month an explosive device that
OL,7,Fpolice described as "crude but viable"
OL,8,Fwas at the centre of an attempted
OL,9,Fattack on another PSNI station in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,FA delivery driver was forced at
OL,13,Fgunpoint to transport the device to
OL,14,FLurgan police station in an incident
OL,15,Fblamed on dissident republicans.
OL,17,FThe device did not explode on that
OL,18,Foccasion.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
